Sazka Risks Losing Lottery License, Hospodarske Noviny Reports

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-03-24T06:57:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/sazka-risks-losing-lottery-license-hospodarske-noviny-reports.html
Sazka AS risks losing its lottery
license after some clients complained they haven’t received
their winnings, Hospodarske  Noviny  reported, citing Karel
Korynta, head of the  Finance Ministry ’s lottery department.  The ministry will start proceedings against the company,
which has also defaulted on its bonds and loans, the Prague-
based newspaper wrote.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
 kchamonikola@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at   gserkin@bloomberg.net  